3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The deep learning-based approach for object detection and interception point prediction involves the use of artificial neural networks, which falls under the domain of AI. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The deep learning-based approach involves the use of artificial neural networks, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The closed-loop control system used in the paper falls under the domain of systems and control.
